QuickStart:

    git clone https://github.com/nxgapps/nxgapps.git -b android-5.1 gapps;
    cd gapps;
    make clean; (Remove output)
    make arm; (If you want compile signed flashable NX GApps package for arm)
    make arm64; (If you want compile signed flashable NX GApps package for arm64)
    make x86; (If you want compile signed flashable NX GApps package for x86)
    make x86_64; (If you want compile signed flashable NX GApps package for x86_64)